name: ALI
description:
FOR BLINF PEOPLE TO SEE: illustration in ink pen and black ink ink. Long face, fleshy mouth, small bun nose, eyes small compared to face size, elongated eyebrows, freckles across the upper part of the face (cheekbone, nose and beginning of forehead). Curly hair with small root braids on the left side and large braids on the right side. .

MY STORY:
Hi, I dance for a living. I've been told a lot that I didn't look like I was in the arts business, that my color wasn't compatible or that my hair is very difficult to fix for presentations. They call me to give workshops at conferences and I like it, but what I really like is teaching in my heart, which is my community and be abble to give them wings to fly as high as possible.
